            </p>
            <p>Manathavady, Wayanad, Kerala</p>
            <p>+91 7012888610</p>
            <p>alphae-com@gmail.com</p>
        </div>
        <div class="categories">
            <div class="heading">
                <h2>CATERGORIES</h2>
            </div>
            <P>SmartPhones</P>
            <p>Laptops</p>
